# Issues: __PROJECT_NAME__

> Updated on: __DATE__

This directory records unresolved problems, not completed changes.

## Good candidates for this directory

- blockers
- known risks
- technical debt
- items that need follow-up but will not be solved immediately

## Suggested fields

- title
- severity / priority
- current impact
- temporary workaround
- next-step recommendation
- related docs

## Recommended companion directories

- an in-progress single change belongs under `docs/changes/active/<change-key>/`
- long-lived truth should be captured under `docs/knowledge/`, not here
